title: Quebec City police say there's been a shooting at mosque
text:
AP January 29, 2017, 10:06 PM Quebec City police say there's been a shooting at mosque 
QUEBEC CITY -- Quebec City police say people have died during a shooting at a mosque in the provincial capital. 
Police did not say how many died in the Sunday shooting. Quebec City police spokesman Constable Pierre Poirier said two suspects were arrested.
